This paper is about document retrieval, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses deep learning models, which are often associated with machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI), so cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely categories. Finally, the paper mentions a fact extraction and verification task, which involves analyzing the content of documents, so cs.CV (computer vision) is a less likely but still possible category.
